  "meta": {
    "name": "DWM1 demo content — S53 regression baseline",
    "schema_version": 1,
    "notes": [
      "Re-expresses the user-confirmed hand-authored custom content of",
      "patches/bank_060.asm, bank_071.asm, the bank_017.asm render regions",
      "and the wram.asm step-counter region as compiler input.",
      "With build.compat.master_table_rooms present, the generated patched",
      "ROM is byte-identical to the S53 reference build (md5",
      "3a5a514c65b330e2788170c5d409b960 as of S53).",
      "Removing build.compat emits the FIXED full-width script master table",
      "(+ shared no-op entry) that closes the S53 scroll-overshoot defect."
    ]
  },

